ce:section.ce:para:
The kinetics plot is obtained by plotting ln (Co/Ct) vs time t for AB and TB dyes as shown in Fig(S5,S6). It explains the degradation of dyes in the presence of CDs as catalyst and it is fitted to pseudo first order kinetics as follows;

                                 ln (Co/Ct) = kt

                           Where Co is the initial concentration of dye and Ct – Concentration of dye at time t, k- Rate constant.
